author: Telegraph Video
title: Watch live coverage as Google expected to unveil new smartphones
text: From 1700 BST Google will begin its annual autumn event, where the tech company is anticipated to announce new smartphones in its Nexus range. The devices are expected to include the Nexus 5X and 6P. Some details of the devices have already been leaked in part, including this image of the 5X. Photo of Google Nexus 5 leaked by G+ user Marques In addition, Google is also expected to announce a new version of its Android operating system. Despite the leaks, Google says that it has "some exciting new treats" to unveil. Watch the live stream to find out what they might be. Or follow our coverage on the live blog here.
